description.en:
The motherly instinct is to give back, provide, protect and ensure that all MAMADOGE holders can eat and stay healthy! $MAMADOGE is a deflationary community token and the birth mother of DOGE Coin. I’m so proud of my son!

MAMADOGE rewards holders, by giving back 5% of every transaction! The team of MAMADOGE has set many milestones in place, to burn extra tokens and send sizeable donations for homeless dogs in need!
